eld may suffice for an inflationary scenario as well as\nthe dark matter and dark energy realms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2009 08:20:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2010 10:17:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-18"}
