 for a simple statistically\nsteady dynamo with finite resistivity all eigenvalues obey Re(lambda_k) < 0.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2009 12:15:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
